    "unlock": "sniper",
    "blurb": "An open Sirocco dune field with the fort wedged on the south edge. Every wave pours down from the north over exposed sand \u2014 face one way and watch the open ground, where buried lurkers wait.",
    "newFeatures": [
      "Back-line fort: waves come only from the north",
      "Sand drag slows every stride",
      "Buried sand-lurkers surface mid-field"
    ]
  },
  "ambience": "ash",
  "intro": [
    {
      "title": "Dust Perimeter",
      "lines": [
        "A supply fort on the south rim of the dune sea, four nights from relief \u2014 and the Entropy massing to the north knows it.",
        "There is no rear to guard: the desert behind you is empty. Build one wall, face north, and never lose the open ground in front of it.",
        "Sand slows every stride. Lurkers lie buried in the flats \u2014 they surface when you cross them. Watch the dunes."
      ],
      "art": "siege"
    }
  ],
  "outro": [
    {
      "title": "The Dune Road Holds",
      "lines": [
        "Four dawns of grit and the southern wall still answers.",
        "The dune road is open \u2014 and the frontier remembers who faced the north and kept it so."
      ],
      "art": "dawn"
    }
  ],
